{"tid":1386474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［屌你老母］【反修例】728上環示威45人被控暴動罪　周三早上東區裁判法院提堂","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T02:03:38.000Z","uid":46352,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"835dafbd61a4183025a74b91a4bc3727f99d0679","tid":1386474,"uid":46352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》爭議未平息，上周日(28日)晚上環一帶又發生嚴重警民衝突，警方至今共拘捕49人，他們被扣查至今。據了解，警方今日徵詢律政司意見後，決定起訴當中45人涉嫌暴動等罪行，明日(31日)早上在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，45人均會被控以暴動罪，部分人會被同時控以阻差辦公、襲擊及藏有攻擊性武器；45人中絕大部分是學生，約三分之一是女性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2414511/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91728%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%8145%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E3%80%80%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82?r=cpsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2414511%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591728%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%258145%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2597%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582%3Fr%3Dcpsdfb&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=fa202030\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2414511/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91728%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%8145%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E3%80%80%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82?r=cpsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲講和！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食屎啦，告曬暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i